Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.44,0:00:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见不到矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.35,0:00:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常之无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.68,0:00:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假什么的...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.50,0:00:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.03,0:00:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.95,0:00:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员都已经到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把桌子放到前面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野他...也许在厕所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.89,0:00:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说今天不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.92,0:00:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事不能参加练习了 找人代演一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角都不在怎么开始排练啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.06,0:00:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他叫过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关机中 联系不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,责任感为零
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别介意 那家伙想干的时候还是会认真干的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.54,0:00:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我一直盼着今天的...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果第二天的练习矢野也没有出现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 啊 水地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典吗 去的去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 要穿浴衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.24,0:02:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会邀上矢野他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翘掉了练习 这种场合倒是能出席嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要是来了 一定要好好惩罚他一下 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 给我找下浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?七美也穿的浴衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.42,0:03:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得七美今天特别可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 穿浴衣好合身啊 令人大吃一惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颜色也很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是找表姐借的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的太孩子气了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腮红也非常可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 是杏黄色的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像刚泡过澡一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是浴衣呢 浴衣军团
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 矢野呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他啊 手机一直打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 可能会和邻居一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.79,0:03:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计一会儿就能遇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能来...就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 高桥简直变了个人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 她穿浴衣很好看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说娃娃脸 小个子穿起和服来特别好看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平时的高桥感觉差异好大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.17,0:04:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太可惜了 要是浴衣是学校制服的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能就会很受欢迎了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野到底在干吗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七美 他说可以给你一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.13,0:04:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳 我还在想是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谁一起来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和班上同学一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是和邻居一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙没来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.37,0:04:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 啊...我没问...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.77,0:04:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真坦率啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说矢野没来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙好像不需要朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道这么说是否合适
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不论怎么吵闹或者在旁边做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都根本不会向这边看一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.76,0:04:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说不可企及吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.92,0:05:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者是 有时候感到好空虚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得不管做什么都没用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意穿了浴衣来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一天天数着日子盼望练习日到来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好空虚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七美 要不要吃刨冰 我去买
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.24,0:05:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 还是联系不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 我本来只是想抱怨他不来练习
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是...忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前天 是奈奈的忌日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 还是会难过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不知道这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不知道 一个人在那兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:05:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么人在他周围玩闹对他来说比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥只要把自己的开朗分给他一点就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你穿浴衣很可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能为他做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到他也不知道该说什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 跟踪狂 在我家附近转来转去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.74,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 我不是跟踪狂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓...吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从什么时候开始看着我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找你有事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了在我身边转来转去?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 让我进去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家拒绝变态的拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙...矢野 给我把门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女变态恼羞成怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗 矢野妈妈 我来做你们家白痴儿子的家庭访问
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我开门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了...不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.89,0:07:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.84,0:07:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝尝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在矢野的房间里两个人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好...好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 你来刺探些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来看看你是不是生病了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会以为我生病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为练习一直都没来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那直接问我为什么不去练习不就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.49,0:08:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明翘班了还这么嚣张
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么翘班啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉浸在奈奈的回忆中了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一到夏天就不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.55,0:08:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天大后天的练习我也不想去 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底为什么翘班呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假谁一大早九点钟起得来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我白担心你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有水羊羹吃 也不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是为了吃水羊羹才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你别吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.74,0:08:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛...这不是很精神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.14,0:08:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有...终于见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.54,0:08:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是相册吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.54,0:09:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下 我把不好的照片拿掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫不好的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修学旅行是去的札幌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 让我看看奈奈的照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要看这个干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:23.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了想怎么样呢 我自己也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是毫无防备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.29,0:09:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己现在在哪里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.94,0:09:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但...但是 房门也开着...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窗前也有人经过...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野又是同班同学...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别误会 我们什么也没做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她自己从床上跌下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思吵到您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗 别当真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样 原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来不是奈奈的照片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的照片已经一张都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不能让他有所反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都这样想着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激动不已地去参加练习
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意穿上了浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专门到他家里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这些你根本就不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后天的练习你一定要来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就只能说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅作为同班同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.40,0:10:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 想见你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许矢野非常非常喜欢的人已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许这样很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也许也有特别特别喜欢矢野的人在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.77,0:11:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样正负相抵 不是正好归零了么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不要认为你只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我在注视着你 一直在注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会守护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在注视着你 会一直守护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 不要认为你是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去看道具了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进展很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为山本的卖力演出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙已经靠不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样就靠我的演技来支撑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.03,0:11:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来简单
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是果然什么也没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七美 七美 我们借了两件号衣来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs30}注:工匠等所穿 在领上或后背印有字号的日本短式外衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个颜色比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红的比较可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是红色的比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.12,0:12:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄脏了也不会很明显呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红的...挺好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对是白的好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我这样心动不已的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿白色很合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊 矢野穿什么都好看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿浴衣不也很适合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.64,0:12:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍的很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真后悔没去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过你在注视着我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说过会一直注视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做...做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.32,0:13:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你简直是乱来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么正负相抵等于零 哪有这种道理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这种男孩子的台词 别太自大了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那种说法太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.66,0:13:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口 借我靠一会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应你 会一直注视着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不再是一个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天一眨眼就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我和矢野之间还是没有任何进展
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野这家伙 在这种地方也能睡着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还拿我的书包做枕头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概在做梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么好梦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野会是在做怎样的梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.94,0:14:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是山本的姐姐么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她一起的男人是香川吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我们入学他刚好毕业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙总是和不同的女人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然和那种无可救药的人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 泼了她一脸的水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吵架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.60,0:14:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是和有里一个班的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.36,0:14:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 你们能借我点钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我男朋友他没有付钱就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.01,0:14:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加那么多的辣酱很像血耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:14:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.15,0:15:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本姐姐和妹妹不太像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定觉得我是傻瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔倒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我男朋友他每次心情不好就会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像小孩子一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的男朋友风评不太好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是人很帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗话说男人不坏女人不爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且人无完人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我能理解他就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.54,0:15:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种就叫做盲目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有真正喜欢过谁吧 你这就叫做乳臭未干哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也赶快谈个真正的恋爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.23,0:15:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈在等男朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暖和的地方等不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.07,0:15:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看她 小心又被借钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去竹家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去换个衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 Sunday出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.25,0:16:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣 笑死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是认为他会来么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么还在等呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了积攒怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,积攒怨恨 然后咒死他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看女人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 那不是暖炉 是饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他先说的 不要和别的男人说话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就回嘴说 你都和别的女人上床了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我就被揍了 那家伙完全就是乐在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每一次哭 他都认为"又有女人为他哭泣了"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一幅自我陶醉的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我诅咒你从桥上掉下来 脖子摔断 头被翻斗车碾碎 最后死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你也觉得我是傻瓜对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底怎么办才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的事自己考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是傻瓜 所以不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你一定要照我说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说...要让我幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福...到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.60,0:17:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是 没有人哭泣和生气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会打人和扔东西...这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们两个人一起去寻找幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个是豆包 我要换啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.83,0:17:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗你的 给你一半
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这样就是幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一阵分手的时候 我甩下了一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福就像是寒冷天气的热可可呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 人都已经回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会成为回忆的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是万一被人看到会引起轩然大波的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天就毕业的所以没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有一年才毕业
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被贴在告示板上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海 想去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 那么冷而且还有腥味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 带我去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊 不要啊 还有海带味 和我想象的根本不一样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虫子 这里也有 讨厌讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是才刚来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去回去回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小野 元晴 生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想看美丽的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什么时候带你去南边的岛屿玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要存钱...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.68,0:19:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点一滴的...大概要等到十年后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 今天就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你拿点东西喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.83,0:19:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和他见面了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是见面了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.92,0:20:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了只是见面而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香川 有学弟找你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学弟?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔跤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.43,0:20:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能呢 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那赢了还是输了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这和输赢无关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打到消气为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是被打到消气为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼 不要碰啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.65,0:20:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想把这个拍下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是为我而战的证据啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和那个自我陶醉的白痴男一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其实根本就是喜欢哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上不会有喜欢哭的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.23,0:21:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我现在才会这么做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答应我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.85,0:21:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.25,0:21:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会再有下一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会背叛你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.14,0:21:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元晴 你冷静地听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...奈奈和香川一起坐车...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.02,0:22:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.96,0:22:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 把你的书包当枕头了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫醒我就行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看着你的睡脸 好像做了很幸福的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.67,0:22:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不忍心叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福的梦...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福...到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.45,0:22:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢 好难的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.56,0:22:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 很温暖的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温暖?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 像肉包子烤地瓜之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寒冷的时候能够温暖人心的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:22:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 也可以是喜欢的书啊CD什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.33,0:23:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者...喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.03,0:23:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃肉包子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉包子的季节到了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次...第一次为某个人的幸福衷心地祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.73,0:25:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢的人最近总是对我很冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.15,0:25:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错觉么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.47,0:25:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从一起吃了肉包子那天以来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.70,0:25:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再像刚才那样过度护着我了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.75,0:25:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.35,0:25:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...弄不懂矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.15,0:25:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是已经不能像以前那样交谈了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.47,0:25:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只说一次 你听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.76,0:25:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你

